polito.sdp2017.Components

Class MappedIP

  • java.lang.Object
    • polito.sdp2017.Components.MappedIP

  • public class MappedIP
extends java.lang.Object
    This class describes the object IP when it is mapped into the FPGA. In fact it's characterized by the object IPCore itself, an unique id for that configuration, a priority and a physical address, both of them chosen by the final user.
